728343f-a.title: Richmond: Arbutus Avenue - Hylan Boulevard
728343f-a.text:
S61 Arbutns Ave., south of the S.E. corner of Hylan Boulevard (Huguenot). This house was occupied by Doty (1874 to 1887) and later (1898) by Stein. The dates refer to maps on which the owners'
names appear.
May 14, 1932.
P. L. Sperr.
